{
  "stem": "2833.3",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So when we came to the barracks we were told to get to the counting early morning and taken to the factory by SS women.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there in the factory, we worked with a group of Polish girls who were also in Auschwitz before, and were supposed to build airplanes.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "None of them ever went up in the air, believe me.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Not the way we worked.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we were locked in.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we worked 12, 14 hours, then we were taken back to the barrack.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then we got dinner, which was again, a piece of bread and some soup, but a little more than, than in Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And unfortunately, I was with two sisters from Prague who one of them wanted to be-- well, she wanted to help herself a little more than she should have, and started to tell about us to the SS commandant of our group.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "She even told on her own sister.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Not always true, but something every morning when he counted us, she reported to him.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "She was put in charge by him, got a little more food, and we got a little beating every time, and even her sister.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So that was a very unpleasant, unfortunate time, because it's one of your own, which hurts even more.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She's, she's still alive and [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I don't-- I don't want to tell.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] she didn't have a happy life afterwards, believe me.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I got a lot of beatings.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And one of the SS women who guarded us in the factory was very, very kind to us.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
